{{fr-infl-adj|sm=gourmand|sf=gourmande|pm=gourmands|pf=gourmandes|smp=ɡuʁ.mɑ̃|sfp=ɡuʁ.mɑ̃d|pmp=ɡuʁ.mɑ̃|pfp=ɡuʁ.mɑ̃d}}
